#: ../../P/pessimal.rst:5
msgid "pessimal"
msgstr "pessimal"

#: ../../P/pessimal.rst:7
msgid "/pes´im·l/, adj\\."
msgstr "/pes´im·l/, 形容詞"

#: ../../P/pessimal.rst:9
msgid ""
"[Latin-based antonym for optimal] Maximally bad. \"This is a pessimal "
"situation.\" Also pessimize vt. To make as bad as possible. These words are "
"the obvious Latin-based antonyms for optimal and optimize, but for some "
"reason they do not appear in most English dictionaries, although ‘pessimize’"
" is listed in the OED."
msgstr ""
"[optimalのラテン語由来の反意語]最大限に悪い。「これはpessimalな状況だ」pessimize "
"他動詞も。可能な限り悪くすること。これらの語はoptimalとoptimizeの明白なラテン語由来の反意語だが、なぜかほとんどの英語辞書には載っていない。ただし‘pessimize’はOEDに収録されている。"
